{
  "text": "We obtained an algebraic characterization of F O[<]-definable regular tree languages in terms of pseudovarieties of preclones, as is reported in [CITATION_1] . A detailed report of this result will appear in [CITATION_2] , and the present paper lays the foundations for this proof.",
